OL,3,CNine officers to face disciplinary
OL,4,Caction for alleged racial
OL,5,Cdiscrimination
OL,7,FNine Greater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,8,Fofficers are to face disciplinary
OL,9,Fhearings after an investigation into
OL,10,Falleged racial discrimination.
OL,12,FEight officers, based in Bury, have
OL,13,Fbeen suspended and one placed on
OL,14,Frestricted duties after an alleged off-
OL,15,Fduty incident.
OL,17,FIt relates to alleged mocking of the
OL,18,Fofficer's accent and other comments
OL,19,Fdirected to them.
