OL,5,Cdiscrimination
OL,7,FThe case is being investigated
OL,8,Finternally by GMP's Professional
OL,9,FStandards Directorate. All of the
OL,10,Fofficers are to face disciplinary
OL,11,Fhearings.
OL,13,FIn a statement GMP said: "We have
OL,14,Fdetermined that nine officers have a
OL,15,Fcase to answer for gross misconduct
OL,16,Ffollowing an internal investigation
OL,17,Finto alleged racial discrimination
OL,18,Fagainst an officer on the Bury
OL,19,Fdistrict.
