OL,3,CNine officers to face disciplinary
OL,4,Caction for alleged racial
OL,5,Cdiscrimination
OL,7,F"Our Professional Standards
OL,8,FDirectorate launched an investigation
OL,9,Fin July 2024 after a report was made
OL,10,Fthat an officer had been subjected to
OL,11,Fracist remarks by some colleagues in
OL,12,FDecember 2023.
OL,14,F"We suspended eight officers who
OL,15,Fremain off duty. A ninth officer has
OL,16,Fbeen restricted from working in Bury
OL,17,Fduring our investigation.
OL,19,F"Work is ongoing to set a date for a
OL,20,Fmisconduct hearing at the earliest
OL,21,Favailable opportunity."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
