OL,3,CNine officers to face disciplinary
OL,4,Caction for alleged racial
OL,5,Cdiscrimination
OL,7,FMeanwhile another five officers from
OL,8,Fthe same division also accused of
OL,9,Fracial discrimination are still being
OL,10,Finvestigated by a watchdog.
OL,12,FThese allegations involve five
OL,13,Fofficers and stem from alleged
OL,14,F'canteen' banter. The subject of their
OL,15,Fcomments was not present or aware of
OL,16,Fwhat was said.
OL,18,FOne officer Scott Dixon was sacked
OL,19,Fafter using the word 'g*lliwog' in
OL,20,Freference to a fellow officer as part
OL,21,Fof the probe.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
