OL,3,CNine officers to face disciplinary
OL,4,Caction for alleged racial
OL,5,Cdiscrimination
OL,7,FThe other four officers have been
OL,8,Fsuspended. The police watchdog - the
OL,9,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,10,F(IOPC) - is taking the lead on that
OL,11,Finquiry.
OL,13,FThe GMP statement adds: "We are aware
OL,14,Fof the Independent Office for Police
OL,15,FConduct (IOPC)'s separate
OL,16,Finvestigation into an unrelated
OL,17,Fincident involving seven officers on
OL,18,Fthe Bury district ` four of whom
OL,19,Fremain suspended. We remain fully
OL,20,Fengaged in supporting the IOPC's
OL,21,Fenquiries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
