OL,5,Cdiscrimination
OL,7,F"The allegations that were made last
OL,8,Fsummer were deeply concerning and we
OL,9,Fhave acted sensitively and
OL,10,Finvestigated thoroughly to ensure that
OL,11,Fthese matters are properly addressed.
OL,13,F"Both victims continue to receive our
OL,14,Ffull support. We have worked
OL,15,Fextensively with officers, staff and
OL,16,Fthe community in Bury to improve
OL,17,Fcultural awareness and ensure that GMP
OL,18,Fis the best it can be for the public
OL,19,Fthat is serves."
