OL,7,FDet Chf Supt Mike Allen, head of
OL,8,FProfessional Standards for GMP, said:
OL,9,F"The GMP and IOPC investigations
OL,10,Frelate to deeply concerning
OL,11,Fallegations into racist remarks about
OL,12,Ftwo officers in unrelated incidents.
OL,13,FWe have conducted a thorough
OL,14,Finvestigation and have fully supported
OL,15,Fthe IOPC with their work, too.
