OL,5,Cdiscrimination
OL,7,F"Ensuring we uphold the highest
OL,8,Fstandards of professional behaviour
OL,9,Facross GMP is essential, and it is
OL,10,Fonly right that when matters such as
OL,11,Fthese are reported to us, we take all
OL,12,Fnecessary action. We now await the
OL,13,Foutcomes of these ongoing proceedings."
OL,15,FChf Supt Kirsty Oliver, district
OL,16,Fcommander for Bury said: "Since being
OL,17,Faware of these allegations last
OL,18,Fsummer, I have shared the shock and
OL,19,Fconcern shown by my officers, staff,
OL,20,Fand the local community.
