OL,7,F"We have worked tirelessly to ensure
OL,8,Fthat the necessary action from our
OL,9,Fprofessional standards team has not
OL,10,Fimpacted on our day-to-day service to
OL,11,Fthe people of Bury. We have continued
OL,12,Fto attend all emergency and priority
OL,13,Fincidents on time, and are getting
OL,14,Fmore justice for victims of crimes
OL,15,Fsuch as personal theft and burglary to
OL,16,Fkeep our town safe."
